Package: render1-dev
Version: 0.8
Revision: 1
BuildDepends: x11-dev
Depends: x11
Source: http://freedesktop.org/~xlibs/release/render-%v.tar.gz
Source-MD5: 69233e5fc7cafb3a154447e2eb76ffe7
ConfigureParams: --prefix=%p/lib/render1 --sysconfdir=/private/etc --bindir=%p/bin --mandir=%p/share/man
InstallScript: <<
 make -j1 install DESTDIR=%d
 install -d -m 755 %i/share/doc/%n
 mv %i/lib/render1/share/doc/render/* %i/share/doc/%n/
 rm -rf %i/lib/render1/share
<<
DocFiles: COPYING ChangeLog INSTALL README
License: OSI-Approved
Description: Headers and documentation for the X render extension
Maintainer: Benjamin Reed <ranger@befunk.com>
Homepage: http://freedesktop.org/~xlibs/
DescPackaging: <<
This package should not be linked against unless absolutely
necessary.  If you must link against it, you need to set
some variables.

  CPPFLAGS:        add -I%p/lib/render1/include
  CFLAGS:          you might need the same as CPPFLAGS
  PKG_CONFIG_PATH: add %p/lib/render1/lib/pkgconfig
<<
